 bathroom. The corridor leads to an airy gallery that can be used as a studio or study, for example. An attractive wooden staircase leads to the impressive living and dining area on the ground floor. An indoor fireplace provides great comfort. Numerous floor-to-ceiling window fronts and glass doors offer optimal lighting conditions and underline the spaciousness of the room. The kitchen is equipped with high-quality appliances and a bright interior. It offers plenty of storage space. In the basement there are two further bedrooms with a shower and toilet.Access to the extremely well-kept garden with lush trees, bushes and shrubs is possible from all floors. The covered outdoor seating area with an outdoor fireplace is on the same level as the ground floor and shines with a fantastic, unobstructable view over Füllinsdorf, Basel and Alsace.Have we aroused your interest in this unique property? We are at your disposal for further information or a visit on site. Note: The information in this sales documentation has been compiled to the best of our knowledge and belief. Deviations are reserved.                                    Nutzfläche: 474.00 m², Anzahl der Schlafzimmer: 3, Anzahl der Badezimmer: 2, Anzahl der separaten WCs: 3, Balkon-Terrassen-Fläche: 47.70 m², 3 Etagen', '\"Architektonisch beachtenswert\" - Luxushaus mit traumhafter Aussicht', 'https://media-pics2.immowelt.org/9/0/F/1/600_4FB28333904043D4A746F2DF466B1F09.jpg,https://media-pics1.immowelt.org/4/D/2/6/600_7D29ACE7BF97452E83F13ECF9B3762D4.jpg,https://media-pics1.immowelt.org/0/D/F/9/600_FAA59FFDD6F644F99464732709D39FD0.jpg,https://media-pics2.immowelt.org/B/9/3/F/600_C12B26809D174CBF8C7E001F7467F39B.jpg,https://media-pics2.immowelt.org/A/A/C/7/600_FF5EAAE3CEC24EEA9A1E0F0A76C67CAA.jpg,https://media-pics1.immowelt.org/6/F/B/1/600_6574CF1EBA1147AD81003CEDE9E41BF6.jpg,https://media-pics2.immowelt.org/A/C/D/B/600_735E171E01184E2EA7B1C6D6585FBDCA.jpg,https://media-pics2.immowelt.org/B/6/E/F/600_74F84EB2CC0F