(172, 'https://www.spiti24.gr/en/1367561', '2018-12-03', 'Greece', 'Athens-Center', 'Ano Kipseli - Evelpidon (Athens)', 37.9973, 23.7362, NULL, 85, NULL, 2, 80000, 'EUR', 'Outstanding apartment, located in the heart of kypseli, near Agios Georgios square, typical in style of the elegant decade of the fifties.Kypseli is one of the oldest historic Athenian neighbourhoods, being in the past a top residential area for the upper class built in a neoclassical and eclectic style. This charming ground floor property occupies an area of 85 sq.m. offering a living room, kitchen, two bedrooms, a bathroom, a w/c and two indoor storage rooms.Being double faced the bedrooms open out onto a beautiful back yard.The heating system is currently a central one powered by oil, however an autonomous gas powered system can be installed, given that the necessary adaptation work will be done. It comes with an asking price of 80.000€', 'Apartment for sale - Kipseli, Ano Kipseli - Evelpidon', 'https://m1.spitogatos.gr/151567014_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m3.spitogatos.gr/151567016_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m2.spitogatos.gr/151567018_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m3.spitogatos.gr/151567019_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m1.spitogatos.gr/151567020_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m2.spitogatos.gr/151567021_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m3.spitogatos.gr/151567022_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m1.spitogatos.gr/151567023_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m3.spitogatos.gr/151567025_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m1.spitogatos.gr/151567026_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m2.spitogatos.gr/151567027_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m3.spitogatos.gr/151567028_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m1.spitogatos.gr/151567029_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m3.spitogatos.gr/151567031_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m1.spitogatos.gr/151567032_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m2.spitogatos.gr/151567033_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m3.spitogatos.gr/151567034_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m1.spitogatos.gr/1515670