(174, 'https://www.spiti24.gr/en/5228279', '2018-06-22', 'Greece', 'Athens-Center', 'Kato Patisia (Athens)', 38.0058, 23.7316, NULL, 129, NULL, 2, 100000, 'EUR', 'Elegant two bedroom flat of the early fifties, 129 sq.m., third floor, in the Athens area of Patisia, 6 minutes walking distance from the metro station of Agios Nicalaos on sale. It was originaly constructed in 1950 bearing the atmospere of this graceful period, while it is maintained in an excellent shape as it is ready to be inhabited with no renovating work needed. The flat is overwhelmed by physical ligth throughout the day and consists of a huge living room area ( a third bedroom can be constructed , should the floor plan be modified), tow spacious bedrooms, a full bathroom, and a kithcen room ideal to be used as a second family sitting room. The apartment also features parque flooring, wooden interior doors, double glazed windows, independent heating system powered by oil, airconditionig units. It comes fully furnished and equipped. The building bears no elevator. Asking price 77.000€', 'Apartment for sale - Patision - Acharnon, Kato Patisia', 'https://m3.spitogatos.gr/137447477_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m2.spitogatos.gr/137447479_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m3.spitogatos.gr/137447480_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m2.spitogatos.gr/137447482_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m3.spitogatos.gr/137447483_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m2.spitogatos.gr/137447485_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m3.spitogatos.gr/137447486_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m1.spitogatos.gr/137447487_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m2.spitogatos.gr/137447488_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m3.spitogatos.gr/137447489_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m2.spitogatos.gr/137447491_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m3.spitogatos.gr/137447492_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m1.spitogatos.gr/137447493_900x675.jpg?v=20130730,https://m3.spitogatos.gr/137447495_900x675.jpg?v=20130730', 0),
